ears of Dannebrog {{!}} The story of the Danish flag|website=Denmark.dk|language=en|access-date=2020-03-28}}</ref>\n* {{flagof|Kuwait|name=''Derti''}} (\"My Nation/Land\"), Kuwait\n\n==E==\n* {{flagof|Greenland|name=''Erfalasorput''}} (\"Our flag\"), Greenland\n* {{flagof|Chile|name=''La Estrella Solitaria''}} (\"The Lonely Star\"), Chile,\n* {{flagof|Cuba|name=''La Estrella Solitaria''}} (\"The Lonely Star\"), Cuba\n* {{flagof|image=Estelada blava.svg|link=Estelada|name=''Estelada blava''}} (\"Blue-Starred Flag\"), [[Catalan separatism]]\n* {{flagof|image=Eureka Flag.svg|link=Eureka Flag|name=Eureka Flag}}, Australia\n\n==F==\n* {{flagof|image=In-jain.svg|link=Jain flag|name=''Five Coloured Flag''}}, Jain flag\n* {{flagof|Quebec|name=''Fleurdelis\u00e9''}} (\"[[Fleur-de-lis]]-y\"), Quebec\n\n==G==\n* {{flagof|Greece|name=''Galanolefki''}} (\"Light blue and white\"), Greece\n* {{flagof|Guyana|name=Golden Arrowhead}}, Guyana\n* {{flagof|Brittany|link=Flag of Brittany|name=''Gwenn-ha-du''}} (\"White and black\"), Brittany\n* {{flagof|United States|1896|name=''Grand Ol' Flag''}}, United States\n* {{Flagof|United States|1776|link=Grand Union Flag|name=''Grand Union Flag''}}, United States\n\n==H==\n* {{flagof|Japan|name=''Hinomaru'' \u65e5\u306e\u4e38}} (\"Sun disc\"), Japan (national flag and [[Rising Sun Flag|naval flag]])\n* {{flagof|Iceland|variant=old|name=''Hv\u00edtbl\u00e1inn''}} (\"The White-blue\"), a flag proposal which was used but never became official, [[Iceland]]\n\n==I==\n* {{flagof|Basque Country|name=''Ikurri\u00f1a''}} (\"Flag\"), Basque Country (the [[Basque Country (autonomous community)|autonomous community]], the [[Basque Country (greater region)|region]], and more generally the [[Basque people|Basque people, culture and language]])\n* {{flagof|Qatar|name=''Innabi''}} (\"The Maroon\"), Qatar\n* {{flagof|India|name=''Tiranga''}} (\"The Tricolour\"), India\n* {{flagof|Ireland|name=''Bratach''}} (\"Irish tricolour\"), Ireland\n* {{flagof|Iran|name=''