colour Flag\"), Azerbaijan\n* {{flagof|Haiti|link=}} ''L'Union Fait La Force'' (\"[[Unity makes strength]]\"), motto on the [[flag of Haiti]]\n* {{flagof|United Kingdom|link=Union Jack|name=''Union Jack''}} or ''Union Flag'',{{efn|Called the \"Royal Union Flag\" in Canada, a former colony of the United Kingdom and current Dominion.}} [[Flag of the United Kingdom|United Kingdom]]\n* {{flagof|United States|link=Jack of the United States|image=US Naval Jack.svg|name=''Union Jack''}}, United States\n\n==W==\n* {{flagof|image=Banner of the Qulla Suyu.svg}} ''[[Wiphala]]'', a flag representing the native peoples of the Andes and the co-official [[flag of Bolivia]]\n*  {{flagof|China|name=\u4e94\u661f\u7ea2\u65d7}} (''W\u01d4 X\u012bng H\u00f3ng Q\u00ed'') (\"Five-Starred Red Flag\"), People's Republic of China\n\n==Y==\n* {{flagof|Wales|name=''Y Ddraig Goch''}} (\"The Red Dragon\"), Wales\n* {{flagof|Confederate States of America|1863|name=''The White Man's Flag''}}, Confederate States\n* {{flagof|Armenia|name=''\u0535\u057c\u0561\u0563\u0578\u0582\u0575\u0576''}} (''Yerakooyn'') (\"Tricolour\"), Armenia\n\n==Z==\n* {{flagof|Ukraine|name=''\u0436\u043e\u0432\u0442\u043e-\u0431\u043b\u0430\u043a\u0438\u0442\u043d\u0438\u0439 (\u043f\u0440\u0430\u043f\u043e\u0440)''}} (''Zhovto-blakytnyy [prapor]'') (\"Yellow-blue [flag]\"), Ukraine\n\n==Notes==\n{{Notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Lists and galleries of flags| Names]]\n[[Category:Lists of names|flag names]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Refimprove|date=January 2014}}\n{{Copy to Wikimedia Commons|date=June 2012}}\n{{Expand list|date=November 2012}}\nThis is an incomplete list of the names and [[nickname]]s of flags, organized in alphabetical order by flag name. Very few flags have any truly official names, but some unofficial names are so widely used that they are accepted as a flag's universal name. \n\n{{Alphanumeric TOC}}\n\n==A==\n* {{flagof|Brazil|name=''A Auriverde''}} (\"The Gold and Green\"), Brazil\n* {{flagof|Greenland|name=''Aappalaartoq''}} (\"The red\"), Greenland\n* {{flagof|Qatar|name=''Al-Adaam''}} (\"Support flag\"), Qatar\n* {{flagof|Kuwait|name=''Alam Baladii''}} (\"My country's flag\"), Kuwait\n* {{flagof|Kurdistan|name=''Alay Reng\u00een''}} (\"Colourful flag\"), Iraqi Kurdistan\n* {{flagof|Turkey|name=''Albayrak''}} (\"Red Flag\"), Turkey\n* {{flagof|Turkey|name=''Alsancak''}} (\"Holy Red Standard\"), Turkey\n* {{flagof|Turkey|name=''Ay Y\u0131ld\u0131z''}} (\"Crescent Star\"), Turkey\n* {{flagof|Argentina|name=''La Albiceleste''}} or ''La Celeste y Blanca'' (\"The white and light blue one\"), Argentina\n* {{flagof|Syria|name=''A'najmataynee''}} (\"The Two Stars\"), Syria\n* {{flagof|Otago|name=''Auld Stobbie''}}, Otago\n\n==B==\n* {{flagof|Brazil|name=''Bandeira Auriverde''}} (\"Gold and green flag\"), Brazil\n* {{flagof|Portugal|name=''Bandeira das Quinas''}} (\"Flag of the ''quinas''\", the five blue shields of the [[Coat of arms of Portugal|Portuguese arms]]), Portugal\n* {{flagof|Portugal|name=''Bandeira Verde-Rubra''}} (\"Green-Red Flag\"), Portugal\n* {{flagof|image=Flag of Saint David.svg|link=Flag of Saint David|name=''Baner Dewi Sant''}} (\"Flag of Saint David\"), Wales (unofficial flag)\n* {{flagof|Cornwall|name=''Baner Peran''}} (\"St. Piran's flag\"), Cornwall\n* {{flagof|California|name=''Bear Flag''}}, California\n* {{Flagof|United States|1777|name=''Betsy Ross Flag''|link=Betsy Ross Flag}}, United States\n* {{flagof|Maratha Empire|name=''Bhagwa''}} (\"The Saffron Banner\"), Flag of the Hindus and former flag of the [[Maratha Empire]]\n* {{flagof|Poland|name=''Bia\u0142o-Czerwona''}} (\"White-Red\"), Poland\n* {{flagof|Belarus|variant=1991|section=White-red-white flag|name=''Bie\u0142-\u010cyrvona-Bie\u0142y''}} (\"White-Red-White\"), former flag of Belarus\n* {{flagof|Austria|name=''Bindenschild''}}, Austria\n* {{flagof|Sweden|name=''Bl\u00e5gul''}} (\"Blue-Gold\" or \"Blue-Yellow\"), Sweden