elle]]\n*[[Ronald Radd]]\n*[[Michael Radford]]\n*[[John Rae (actor)|John Rae]]\n*[[Michael Rathborne]]\n*[[Bill Reed (actor)|Bill Reed]]\n*[[Geoffrey Reed (actor)|Geoffrey Reed]]\n*[[Cyril Renison]]\n*[[Marjorie Rhodes]]\n*[[John Richmond (actor)|John Richmond]]\n*[[Michael Ripper]]\n*[[Colin Rix]]\n*[[Anton Rodgers]]\n*[[Edina Ronay]]\n*[[Adrian Ropes]]\n*[[Jan Rossini]]\n*[[Robert Russell (English actor)|Robert Russell]]\n*[[Madge Ryan]]\n*[[Paddy Ryan (actor)|Paddy Ryan]]\n'''S'''\n*[[Andrew Sachs]]\n*[[Anthony Sagar]]\n*[[Leslie Schofield]]\n*[[Alex Scott (actor)|Alex Scott]]\n*[[George Sewell]]\n*[[Cyril Shaps]]\n*[[Ann Sharp]]\n*[[John Sharp (actor)|John Sharp]]\n*[[Michael Sheard]]\n*[[David Sinclair (actor)|David Sinclair]]\n*Kevin Smith\n*[[Walter Sparrow]]\n*[[William Squire]]\n*[[Tony Steedman]]\n*[[Peter Stephens (actor)|Peter Stephens]]\n*[[David Stoll (actor)|David Stoll]]\n*[[John Styles]]\n*[[Dudley Sutton]]\n*[[Ingrid Sylvester]]\n'''T'''\n*[[Larry Taylor (actor)|Larry Taylor]]\n*[[Nigel Terry]]\n*[[Tony Thawnton]]\n*[[Hilary Tindall]]\n*[[John A. Tinn]]\n*[[Frederick Treves (actor)|Frederick Treves]]\n'''V'''\n*[[Colin Vancao]]\n*[[Peter Vaughan]]\n*[[Sue Vaughan]]\n*[[Don Vernon]]\n'''W'''\n*[[John Walker (actor)|John Walker]]\n*[[Gary Watson]]\n*[[Kenneth Watson]]\n*[[David Webb (anti-censorship campaigner)|David Webb]]\n*[[Timothy West]]\n*[[Phillip Weston]]\n*[[Les White (actor)|Les White]]\n*[[Frank Windsor]]\n*[[Beverly Winn]]\n*[[Hilary Wontner]]\n*[[Betty Woolfe]]\n*[[Jack Woolgar]]\n*[[Katya Wyeth]]\n'''Y'''\n*[[Jeremy Young]]\n*[[Raymond Young]]\n'''Z'''\n*[[Nick Zaran]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n{{hidden end}}\n\n==Episode list==\n\nAirdates given here are for [[LWT]] (London). It was the only ITV station to screen all 26 episodes without breaks in transmission. Other [[ITV (TV network)|ITV]] regions varied airdates and transmission order.\n\nFilming took place between May 1968 and July 1969.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-style=