ry Duggan]]\n*[[William Dysart]]\n'''E'''\n*[[Clifford Earl]]\n*[[Meredith Edwards (actor)|Meredith Edwards]]\n*[[Christopher Eedy]]\n*[[Peter Jay Elliott]]\n*[[Eva Enger]]\n*[[Norman Eshley]]\n*[[Clifford Evans (actor)|Clifford Evans]]\n*[[Tenniel Evans]]\n'''F'''\n*[[Max Faulkner (actor)|Max Faulkner]]\n*[[Gerald Flood]]\n*[[David Forbes (actor)|David Forbes]]\n*[[Michael Forrest]]\n*[[Dudley Foster]]\n*[[Grazina Frame]]\n*[[John Fraser (actor)|John Fraser]]\n*[[Liz Fraser]]\n'''G'''\n*[[Chris Gannon (actor)|Chris Gannon]]\n*[[John Garvin (actor)|John Garvin]]\n*[[Sue Gerrard]]\n*[[Alan Gifford]]\n*[[Michael Goldie]]\n*[[Michael Goodliffe]]\n*[[Howard Goorney]]\n*[[Romo Gorrara]]\n*[[Michael Gothard]]\n*[[Michael Gover]]\n*[[Michael Graham (actor)|Michael Graham]]\n*[[Danny Green (actor)|Danny Green]]\n*[[Earl Green]]\n*[[Keith Grenville]]\n*[[Michael Gwynn]]\n'''H'''\n*[[Patricia Haines]]\n*[[John Hallam]]\n*[[Olivia Hamnett]]\n*[[Doris Hare]]\n*[[Juliet Harmer]]\n*[[John Harvey (actor)|John Harvey]]\n*[[Robin Hawdon]]\n*[[David Healy (actor)|David Healy]]\n*[[Thomas Heathcote]]\n*[[Maurice Hedley]]\n*[[Drewe Henley]]\n*[[Patrick Holt]]\n*[[George Howe (actor)|George Howe]]\n*[[Stuart Hoyle]]\n*[[John Hughes (actor)|John Hughes]]\n*[[Geoffrey Hughes]]\n*[[Peter Hughes (actor)|Peter Hughes]]\n*[[Harry Hutchinson (actor)|Harry Hutchinson]]\n\n'''I'''\n*[[Barrie Ingham]]\n*[[Harold Innocent]]\n'''J'''\n*[[Freda Jackson]]\n*[[Philip James (actor)|Philip James]]\n*[[David Jason]]\n*[[Clare Jenkins]]\n*[[Peter Jesson]]\n*[[Robin John]]\n*[[Dudley Jones]]\n*[[John Glyn-Jones]]\n*[[Peter Jones (actor)|Peter Jones]]\n*[[Patrick Jordan]]\n'''K'''\n*[[Bernard Kay]]\n*[[Dermot Kelly (actor)|Dermot Kelly]]\n*[[William Kendall (actor)|William Kendall]]\n*[[John Kidd (actor)|John Kidd]]\n*[[Geoff King]]\n'''L'''\n*[[Ronald Lacey]]\n*[[Charles Lamb (actor)|Charles Lamb]]\n*[[Jack Lambert (British actor)|Jack Lambert]]\n*[[Duncan Lamont]]\n*[[Peter Lawrence (actor)|Peter Lawrence