e-lucky-as-castlerahan-finally-reign-in-cavan/\n| team1 = [[Castlerahan GAA|Castlerahan]] [[File:Colours of Galway.svg|20px|border]]\n| score = 2-11 \u2013 1-13\n| team2 = [[File:Colours of Kilkenny.svg|20px|border]] [[Crosserlough GFC|Crosserlough]]\n| goals1 = O. O'Connell 1-3, S. Brady 1-1, C. Mackey 0-4 (0-4f), E. Flanagan 0-3\n| goals2 = P. Smith 0-5 (0-2f), J. Smith 1-0, P. Lynch (1 '45), S. Smith, M. Stuart 0-2 each, D. Gaffney, P. McEvoy 0-1 each\n| stadium = [[Breffni Park]]\n| referee = Conor Dourneen\n}}\n\n==Relegation Play-Offs==\n\nThe 4 bottom placed teams the league phase will play off against each other. The 2 winners will maintain their senior status for 2019 while the 2 losers will face off in a Relegation-Final. The ultimate loser will be relegated to the 2019 I.F.C.\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| date = 21 September 2018\n| round = Relegation Semi-final\n| team1 = [[Cootehill Celtic GFC|Cootehill]] [[File:Colours of Limerick.svg|20px|border]]\n| score = 1-8 \u2013 1-9\n| team2 = [[File:Colours of Donegal.svg|20px|border]] Shercock\n| goals1 = \n| goals2 =\n| stadium = [[Kingscourt Stars GAA|O'Raghallaigh Park]]\n| referee = Joey Curley\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| date = 23 September 2018\n| round = Relegation Semi-final\n| team1 = [[Killygarry GAA|Killygarry]] [[File:Colours of Down.svg|20px|border]]\n| score = 1-20 \u2013 1-8\n| team2 = [[File:Colours of Antrim.svg|20px|border]] [[Ballinagh GAA|Ballinagh]]\n| goals1 = \n| goals2 =\n| stadium = [[Drumalee GFC|St. Felim's Park]]\n| referee = Pat Clarke\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| date = 29 September 2018\n| round = Relegation Final\n| team1 = [[Cootehill Celtic GAA|Cootehill]] [[File:Colours of Limerick.svg|20px|border]]\n| score = 2-15 \u2013 2-10\n| team2 = [[File:Colours of Antrim.svg|20px|border]] [[Ballinagh GAA|Ballinagh]]\n| goals1 = \n| goals2 =\n| stadium = [[Drumalee GFC|St. Felim's Park]]\n| referee = Margaret Farrelly\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links